:: Hell Beast, Megatron, Black Aracnia, and ( im assuming ) Brightblade set 
down on the beach by Zardus and Liono Prime. :::

::: Hell Beast puts his pistol away and walks up to his nemisis ::: Well 
Liono, were here. Lets begin this discussion. Firstly, we need to cooperate 
fully with each other, otherwise we will get no where and this will all be 
for nothing.

::: Megatron ::: Indeed, this is a very important matter.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~

::: Ominous Prime was in the middle of his first objective. He was going to 
kill Hell Beast. :::

::: Ominous tinkered with a Cyberbee, an old modle but still useful. He 
planted it with an energon virus. It would exploded and infect anybot within 
a hundred meters of it. They would die slowly, very painfully. :::

::: Ra ::: And your going to kill Hell Beast with that...thing?

::: Ominous ::: Yes, and then his team will fight over the next leader and 
the Predacons will fall.

::: Ra ::: How much longer?

::: Ominous hooked a wire to the bomb within, and the bee shot up and darted 
out of the ship. :::

::: Set ::: That was fast....

::: Ominous ::: It goes up to 90 MPH. Hell Beast wont even realize it has hit 
him!
